title: 01/28/2013 - The Church Of What's Happening Now #50
description:
We reached 50 episodes all thanks to you! Gary calls back today to update us on how his life is going after just finishing a 21 year prison sentence. Comedian Steve Simeone calls in and talks to Joey about their days with RJ the eccentric gambler.
